{"timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:54:10.058924Z","level":"info","event":"      • Source system allows NULL values in critical columns (name, email, amount, description).","logger":"task.stdout"}
{"timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:54:10.059186Z","level":"info","event":"      • No business rule enforcement prevents negative transaction amounts.","logger":"task.stdout"}
{"timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:54:10.059459Z","level":"info","event":"      • Description field permits empty strings without validation or trimming.","logger":"task.stdout"}
{"timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:54:10.059693Z","level":"info","event":"","logger":"task.stdout"}
